        "data": "<h1 class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">Service Updates for Liferay Cloud</h1>\n<p>The services update for 02/09/2023 is a patch bump for <strong>backup</strong> service. </p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2>DXP Cloud Stack - 02/02/2023</h2>\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 727px; float: left; height: 350px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 98.8333px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 102.383px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Previous Release</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 101.3px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Current Release</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 379.483px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Docker Images</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody valign=\"top\">\n<tr style=\"height: 48px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 98.8333px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Backup</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 102.383px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.0.2</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 101.3px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.0.3</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 379.483px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>liferaycloud/backup:5.0.3</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 98.8333px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">CI</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 102.383px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.0.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 101.3px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.0.1</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 379.483px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/jenkins:2.319.3-jdk8-5.0.1<strong><br></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 41.2222px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 98.8333px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Database</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 102.383px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.0.2</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 101.3px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.0.3</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 379.483px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/database:5.0.3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 98.8333px; text-align: left; vertical-align: middle; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Liferay</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 102.383px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.0.2</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 101.3px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.0.2</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 379.483px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.4-5.0.2<br>liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.3-5.0.2</p>\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.2-5.0.2</p>\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp7.1-5.0.2</p>\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp7.0-5.0.2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 98.8333px; text-align: left; vertical-align: middle; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Search</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 102.383px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.0.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 101.3px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.0.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 379.483px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">li<span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">feraycloud/elasticse</span></span><span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">arch:7.17.1-5.0.0</span></span><strong><span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">liferaycloud/elasticsearch:6.8.23-5.0.0</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">li<span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">feraycloud/elasticsearch:2.4.6-5.0.0</span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 98.8333px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Webserver</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 102.383px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.0.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 101.3px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.0.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 379.483px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/nginx:1.21.6-5.0.0<br><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2> </h2>\n<h2> </h2>\n<h2> </h2>\n<h2> </h2>\n<h2>Update Instructions</h2>\n<p>Note : To take advantage of the new features and fixes provided by the 5.x stack of services, you must update your entire stack to the new 5.x images.</p>\n<h2>Change Log</h2>\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto; height: 150px; width: 764px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 76.6562px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 59.625px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Version</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 76.5391px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Ticket Number</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 506.18px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Description</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody valign=\"top\">\n<tr style=\"height: 22px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 76.6562px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Backup<br></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 59.625px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.0.3</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-right\" style=\"width: 76.5391px; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">LCD-24311</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 506.18px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\">\n<p>Fix Bug: Backup Id undefined while backup create</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 76.6562px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong> </strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 59.625px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.0.3</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-right\" style=\"width: 76.5391px; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">LCD-14305</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 506.18px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\">Add initial Backup Upload routes (GCS - CLI)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>"
